lemma add_squared (a b : mynat) :

rw two_eq_succ_one,
rw one_eq_succ_zero,
repeat {rw pow_succ},
repeat {rw succ_mul},
repeat {rw zero_mul},
repeat {rw pow_zero},
repeat {rw zero_add},
repeat {rw one_mul},
repeat {rw mul_add},
repeat {rw add_mul},
rw add_assoc (a * a) (b * a),
rw mul_comm b a,
rw add_comm (a * b) (b * b),
rw add_comm (a * b) (b * b + a * b),
rw add_assoc (a * a) (b * b) (a * b + a * b),
rw add_assoc (b * b) (a * b) (a * b),
refl,
